    <p>Welcome to Beav-Guesser! This game challenges your knowledge of the Oregon State University campus.</p>
    
    <h2>How to Play</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Click the "Play" button to start the game.</li>
        <li>You will play 5 rounds, each with a new location on the OSU map.</li>
        <li>For each round, guess the location by placing a marker on the map.</li>
        <li>Points are awarded based on the accuracy of your guess.</li>
        <li>After 5 rounds, your total score will be displayed on the leaderboard.</li>
    </ol>
    <p>Good luck and have fun!</p>

    
    <p>For more detailed instructions, please refer to the <a href="https://github.com/blakethomas12/Beav-Guesser/blob/main/User_Manual.md">User Manual</a>.</p>
